{
  "stem": "1502.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They also deported almost the entire Jewish personnel from the camp, which was there for two years.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was a very brutal transport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There were a lot of screams and beatings, and it was-- it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Matter of fact, that was the last transport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We got the confirmation, like the miracle, we got the confirmation from the Red Cross, with a number, with everything, just a few days before that 26th transport.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "That was 20-- 27th transport.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And again, I was put-- I was postponed for the next transport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I got the new transport number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at that time, I was the only [? flitzer, ?] the only escapee, left.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Mayer had a problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How can you keep one escapee in the hall?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the head of the hall, the leader, the [GERMAN], was deported.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody was deported.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he told me there is no other way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You leave the escapee place, the [? flizter ?] [? is ?] [? out. ?] You go together with your family, and forget that you are [? flitzer. ?]",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The day of the transport he said, make that you don't exist, hide somewhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because if they'll find you, yes papers or no papers, they'll pack you up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hide, don't be in their eyes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans shouldn't see you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After the transport will leave, go in the room with your parents, you-- forget.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You no [? flitzer. ?] And that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After that last transport left, there were very few Jews left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was only one-- one hall, and I went together with my parents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the transport left sometimes in August and they were-- even saw that they had the-- the war was lost for them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Allies were advancing in France.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They broke out from Normandy.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
